{
    "_comment": "VLESS Reverse Proxy bridge（落地机）配置 — 在家宽内网机器上跑，反向连接公网 sb-xray 构建隧道。",
    "_usage": [
        "1. 公网端 sb-xray 必须设置: ENABLE_REVERSE=true（docker-compose environment）",
        "2. 在公网端 sb-xray 容器运行 show-config 脚本，获取 XRAY_REVERSE_UUID / DOMAIN / DEST_HOST / XRAY_REALITY_PUBLIC_KEY / XRAY_REALITY_SHORTID",
        "3. 替换本文件的占位符：${XRAY_REVERSE_UUID} ${DOMAIN} ${LISTENING_PORT} ${DEST_HOST} ${XRAY_REALITY_PUBLIC_KEY} ${XRAY_REALITY_SHORTID}",
        "4. 落地机执行 xray -c reverse_bridge_client.json 跑作为长驻进程（推荐用 systemd unit）",
        "5. 落地机端需要能访问公网 sb-xray（出站 443/TCP）；无需落地机开端口",
        "6. 公网端 routing.rules 里把 REVERSE_DOMAINS 匹配的流量 outboundTag 指向 r-tunnel，流量即反向穿透到落地机 freedom 出口",
        "",
        "详见 docs/08-reverse-proxy-guide.md"
    ],
    "log": {
        "loglevel": "warning"
    },
    "inbounds": [
        {
            "tag": "api",
            "port": 7979,
            "listen": "127.0.0.1",
            "protocol": "dokodemo-door",
            "settings": {
                "address": "127.0.0.1"
            }
        }
    ],
    "outbounds": [
        {
            "protocol": "vless",
            "tag": "reverse-bridge",
            "settings": {
                "address": "${DOMAIN}",
                "port": 443,
                "id": "${XRAY_REVERSE_UUID}",
                "flow": "xtls-rprx-vision",
                "encryption": "none",
                "reverse": {
                    "tag": "r-tunnel"
                }
            },
            "streamSettings": {
                "network": "raw",
                "security": "reality",
                "realitySettings": {
                    "serverName": "${DEST_HOST}",
                    "fingerprint": "chrome",
                    "publicKey": "${XRAY_REALITY_PUBLIC_KEY}",
                    "shortId": "${XRAY_REALITY_SHORTID}",
                    "spiderX": "/"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "tag": "direct",
            "protocol": "freedom",
            "settings": {
                "domainStrategy": "UseIPv4v6"
            }
        }
    ],
    "routing": {
        "rules": [
            {
                "type": "field",
                "inboundTag": ["reverse-bridge"],
                "outboundTag": "direct"
            }
        ]
    }
}
